    "longBusinessSummary": "Al Taiseer Group TALCO Industrial Company engages in the designing, manufacturing, and marketing a range of aluminum products in Oman, Kuwait, Bahrain, Egypt, Iraq, the United Arab Emirates, Lebanon, and internationally. It operates through Aluminum Forming and Selling Sector; Metal Coating Powder Sector; and Other segments. The company offers aluminum extrusion, decorative surface finishes, and thermal break products. It also provides anodized, powder-coated, PVDF coatings; wood-finished aluminum, such as real wood, effecta, film sublimation; thermoset powder coatings, including polyester, epoxy, super durable, and metallic powders; and weatherstrips, polypropylene yarn, rubber gaskets, plastic components, bags, sheets, and wrapping films. Its products are used in architectural products, aluminum profiles, building facades, doors, windows and curtain walls of buildings, kitchens, truck bodies. The company was incorporated in 1976 and is based in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia.",
